title: French Meadow Bakery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of the Minneapolis-based franchise European style cafe and bakery. Has organic and all-natural products including yeast-free, vegan, sprouted grain, gluten-free and Kosher Parve options. Offers a few vegetarian choices including: a vegan chili, 1 or 2 vegan baked goods daily, bread, and house salad.
streetAddress: 776 Terminal Dr, Salt Lake City Airport
